      <div xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2">
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-Hd1e118">I, P. 2, Inq. 2, Tract. 1, Q. 4, C. 2</head>
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-Hd1e121" type="question-title">AN EODEM MODO DICANTUR <mentioned>IUSTUM</mentioned> ET <mentioned>BONUM</mentioned> DE DEO.</head>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-d1e124">
          <pb ed="#P" n="548"/>
          <cb ed="#Q" n="a"/>
          <!-- c2 -->
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Consequenter quaeritur an eodem modo dicantur
          <lb ed="#Q"/><mentioned>iustum</mentioned> et <mentioned>bonum</mentioned> de Deo.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-d1e135">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Quod videtur: 1. Quia utrumque est nomen con<lb ed="#Q"/>sequens
          naturam in ratione quae dicta est<!--1-->; eo<lb ed="#Q"/>dem
          ergo modo dicuntur.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-d1e144">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Contra: a. Nomen boni<!--a--> derivatur ad omnes
          <lb ed="#Q"/>creaturas; unde <name>Boethius</name><!--2-->: <quote>Omnia bona</quote>,
          <lb ed="#Q"/>quia a bono, <quote>iustum autem non</quote>; non enim
          <lb ed="#Q"/>omnia iusta, quia a iusto.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p2i2t1q4c2-d1e156">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Responsio<!--b--> dicta est supra, in<!--c--> Quaestione De 
          <cb ed="#Q" n="b"/>
          <lb ed="#Q"/>bonitate<!--3-->. Nam <mentioned>bonum</mentioned> est conditio generalis
          <lb ed="#Q"/>ipsius causae, quae est Deus: quia enim bonus,
          <lb ed="#Q"/>ideo fecit creaturam; unde <name ref="#Augustine">Augustinus</name><!--4-->:
          <lb ed="#Q"/><quote>Quia bonus est, sumus</quote>; et ideo <mentioned>bonum</mentioned> re<lb ed="#Q"/>spicit
          omnem creaturam cuius est causa. <mentioned>Iu<lb ed="#Q"/>stum</mentioned>
          vero est conditio<!--d--> specialis et respicit spe<lb ed="#Q"/>cialem
          actum, scilicet<!--e--> reddere unicuique quod
          <lb ed="#Q"/>suum est, quod pertinet ad rationalem creatu<lb ed="#Q"/>ram;
          et ideo <mentioned>iustum</mentioned> <quote>non descendit ad om<lb ed="#Q"/>nia</quote>,
          sicut dicit <name>Boethius</name>, in libro<!--f--> <title>De heb<lb ed="#Q"/>domadibus</title><!--5-->.
        </p>
      </div>
